@startuml
actor Pengguna
participant View
participant Controller
participant Model
participant Database

Pengguna -> View : Akses halaman Registrasi
View --> Pengguna : Tampilkan form Registrasi

Pengguna -> View : Pilih role, masukkan data diri\nKlik tombol Daftar
View -> Controller : POST /register (data)

Controller -> Controller : Validasi input data
Controller -> Model : check existing email
Model -> Database : query user by email
Database --> Model : return result
Model --> Controller : return result

alt Data valid & Email belum terdaftar?
    Controller -> Model : create(data)
    Model -> Database : insert user data
    Database --> Model : success
    Model --> Controller : success
    Controller -> Controller : Kirim email verifikasi (opsional)
    Controller --> View : Redirect with success message
    View --> Pengguna : Tampilkan pesan sukses
else Data tidak valid / Email terdaftar
    Controller --> View : Redirect back with error validation
    View --> Pengguna : Tampilkan pesan error validasi & form
end
@enduml
